.SS "Traditional format specifications may be intermixed; they accumulate:"
.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#od-a'\fB\-a\fP\X'tty: link'
same as \fB\-t\fR a,  select named characters, ignoring high\-order bit
.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#od-b'\fB\-b\fP\X'tty: link'
same as \fB\-t\fR o1, select octal bytes
.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#od-c'\fB\-c\fP\X'tty: link'
same as \fB\-t\fR c,  select printable characters or backslash escapes
.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#od-d'\fB\-d\fP\X'tty: link'
